OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,FOvercrowding in British prisons has
OL,7,Fled to calls for magistrates to stop
OL,8,Fjailing criminals for several weeks to
OL,9,Fease pressure.
OL,11,FOne of the country's most senior
OL,12,Fjudges, Lord Justice Green, has told
OL,13,Fmagistrates to delay sentencing
OL,14,Foffenders likely to be jailed until at
OL,15,Fleast September 10.
OL,17,FAs reported in The Times, Green made
OL,18,Fthe advisement in line with Justice
OL,19,FSecrertary Shabana Mahmood's plans to
OL,20,Frelease 2,000 prisoners early next
OL,21,Fmonth.
