OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,FThey said in a statement: "The new
OL,7,Fgovernment inherited a prisons crisis,
OL,8,Fand this is yet another sign of the
OL,9,Fpressures our justice system is
OL,10,Ffacing. The changes coming into force
OL,11,Fin September will bring it under
OL,12,Fcontrol.
OL,14,F"Independent judges decide when to
OL,15,Fschedule court hearings and do so in
OL,16,Fthe interests of justice, including to
OL,17,Fensure the effective operation of the
OL,18,Fcriminal justice system."
