OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,FThe advice did not apply to higher
OL,7,Fcourts dealing with more serious
OL,8,Fcriminal cases. About 2,000 prison
OL,9,Fplaces will be freed up under Labour's
OL,10,Fearly release scheme.
OL,12,FAccording to the government, the
OL,13,Finitiative will free up to 5,500
OL,14,Fprison places in the longer term by
OL,15,Fmoving the standard release date.
OL,17,FPrisoners who were previously eligible
OL,18,Ffor release after serving 50% of their
OL,19,Fsentence could now go free after
OL,20,Fserving just 40% of time behind bars.
