OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,FThe new programme will not apply to
OL,7,Fviolent offenders serving sentences of
OL,8,Ffour years or more, or those convicted
OL,9,Fof domestic violence or sexual
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FMagistrates handled more than 1.3
OL,13,Fmillion cases last year, official
OL,14,Ffigures showed.
OL,16,FTom Franklin, chief executive of the
OL,17,FMagistrates Association, said:
OL,18,F"Another day, another sticking plaster
OL,19,Fto hold our crumbling justice system
OL,20,Ftogether.
