OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,F"While this measure may be necessary
OL,7,Fin the short term, things can't keep
OL,8,Fgoing on like this and we need a long-
OL,9,Fterm plan and an injection of more
OL,10,Fresources at every stage of the
OL,11,Fjustice process for recovery.
OL,13,F"We also need a grown-up discussion
OL,14,Fabout the purpose of prison, and
OL,15,Findeed other types of sentences such
OL,16,Fas community sentences."
