OL,3,CMagistrates told to delay sentencing
OL,4,Cto ease prison overcrowding
OL,6,FIt comes days after emergency plans
OL,7,Fwere greenlit in the North of England.
OL,9,FOperation Early Dawn, a long-standing
OL,10,Fplan that allows defendants to be held
OL,11,Fin police cells and not summoned to
OL,12,Fmagistrates' court until a space in
OL,13,Fprison is available, was activated on
OL,14,FMonday morning.
OL,16,FMeasures were announced in the North
OL,17,FEast and Yorkshire; Cumbria and
OL,18,FLancashire; and Manchester, Merseyside
OL,19,Fand Cheshire regions.
